Package technologyMapping.runtime.environment

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TMArgDescription
    The TMArgDescription class is class containing the description of the command line argument(s) for the technologyMapping stage.
    TMArgString
    The TMArgString class is class containing the string referencing the command line argument(s) for the technologyMapping stage.
    TMRuntimeEnv
    The TMRuntimeEnv class is a class for managing and parsing command line argument(s) for the technologyMapping stage.
